original_title: Chi Chi LaRue's Bachelor Party: The Big Switch 3
overview: Jeanna Fine was one of the first A list girls to star in Bi-sexual movies, bringing them into the forefront. In BACHELOR PARTY: THE BIG SWITCH 3, Jeanna is cast as a good time girl who`s services are booked in for the party. Bride-to-be Tracy Winn is not taking the fact that her fiance is getting some on the side by rolling over, that is until the stripper she hired for a private show tells her to do just that. Hot studs and beautiful babes grace the screen in this third installment from Director Chi Chi LaRue.
title: Chi Chi LaRue's Bachelor Party: The Big Switch 3
